freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: Injection site became red, swollen, and itchy on 2/18. It grew in size overnight into 2/19, despite taking Benadryl orally. I used topical Benadryl over the weekend, which helped. You can still see a bruise-like spot today.

freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: With both my 1st and 2nd shots, the injection area has been hot to the touch, in addition to the symptoms marked previously.
